{"tid":2220993,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"譚詠麟老豆譚江柏曾經去過德國參加奧運足球賽並獲希特拉頒獎呢單野其實堅定流","createTime":"2020-09-28T05:09:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-28T10:19:25.000Z","uid":28765,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"1961603992796fa6041e4bd0d156c32a0ad9b362","tid":2220993,"uid":28765,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:09:57.000Z","msg":"Wiki睇到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n譚江柏（1911年11月27日－2006年3月16日），清宣統三年生於廣州，是1930年代中華民國國家足球代表隊成員、香港球壇名宿，外號「譚銅頭」[1]。譚曾先後效力南華、星島、九巴等香港甲級足球聯賽球隊。乃香港著名歌壇巨星譚詠麟的父親。於2006年3月16日早上七時許，因身體器官功能衰竭在香港養和醫院病逝。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n1936年，代表中華民國前往德國首都柏林參加奧運足球賽，獲當時納粹德國元首希特勒頒授過一隻懷錶。"},{"pid":"b6d1f21d30aa6efdd3c232eeac3c7b8ab65a056e","tid":2220993,"uid":128102,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"佢咁撚種族主義<br />\n唔知佢點睇黃種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9634ebcd92db30a695f8c327bf8f9d0383ecc3a","tid":2220993,"uid":205742,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:21:33.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"3b803262884b063363734456c313bd3336b7b1d5","tid":2220993,"uid":205742,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"e20f55e79b46f6bee42f894b4dd27dc6310e4245","tid":2220993,"uid":128102,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3b803262884b063363734456c313bd3336b7b1d5","tid":2220993,"uid":205742,"like":2,"dislike":2,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b6d1f21d30aa6efdd3c232eeac3c7b8ab65a056e","tid":2220993,"uid":128102,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:12:21.000Z","msg":"佢咁撚種族主義<br />\n唔知佢點睇黃種人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:21:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-28T05:28:00.000Z","msg":"無睇德國奧運佢串尻黑人？<br />\n佢只係最睇唔起猶太人<br />\n個核心係亞利安人優越論"},{"pid":"f104ab2fc6a09